lead_paragraph: Anthony Raspa, who had been on the force for about a year and a half, was killed on Saturday in the crash in Monmouth County, and his partner was injured, the authorities said.
snippet: Anthony Raspa, who had been on the force for about a year and a half, was killed on Saturday in the crash in Monmouth County, and his partner was injured, the authorities said....
abstract: New Jersey State Trooper Anthony Raspa is killed, and his partner Trooper Gene Hong injured, when their patrol car strikes a deer on a highway in Monmouth County and veers off road into a tree.

headline.main: New Jersey State Trooper Killed After Patrol Car Hits Deer
headline.print_headline: New Jersey State Trooper Killed After Patrol Car Hits Deer
